	heroSubhead={`You are the people of the covenant — the people through whom the Scriptures came, and to whom the revelation of God as Father first arrived. Long before anyone else, your own prophets and psalms called Him "our Father." That tender Fatherhood is woven through the Tanakh, an invitation to know the God of Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob not only as Sovereign, but as the One who loves you like a Father loves a child.`}
