	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `It surfaces the Father-heart already in the Tanakh`, bodyHtml: `The Fatherhood of God is not a new idea added on — it is in Isaiah, the Psalms, Hosea, Deuteronomy, Jeremiah, and Malachi. The Father's Heart Bible™ simply lets that nearness be heard clearly, revealing God as Father wherever your own Scriptures already do. Begin where it all begins, in <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a>.` },
